headline: Carrier to Present at the Bank of America Global Industrials Conference
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR) Chairman & CEO David Gitlin and Senior Vice President & CFO Patrick Goris will speak at the Bank of America Global Industrials Conference in London on Thursday, March 20, 2025 at 4:50 a.m. ET.
